c4 Buccaneer Bay Harbor Authority — Containers

tag Technology as tech
  React blue
  Node.js green
  Python orange
  PostgreSQL purple
  Redis red
  Kafka teal

Ship Captain is a person
  description: Requests moorings and files cargo manifests
  -Books berths via [HTTPS]-> Dock Board

Customs Officer is a person
  description: Inspects cargo and assesses duties on incoming loot
  -Assesses duties via [HTTPS]-> Toll Desk

Harbor Authority is a system
  description: Manages berths, manifests, and tolls for the port
  -Fetches tide forecasts from [HTTPS]-> Tide Almanac
  -Settles doubloon tolls through [REST]-> Coin Exchange
  ~Dispatches notices via~> Pigeon Post

  containers
    [Quarterdeck]
      Dock Board is a container tech: React
        description: Berth scheduling console for captains
        -Books berths through [JSON/HTTPS]-> Manifest API

      Toll Desk is a container tech: React
        description: Customs and duty-assessment console
        -Reads manifests through [JSON/HTTPS]-> Manifest API

    [Below Deck]
      Manifest API is a container tech: Node.js
        description: Core API for berths, manifests, and tolls
        -Reads and writes [SQL/TCP]-> Harbor Ledger
        -Caches availability in [RESP]-> Chart Cache
        ~Publishes berth events to~> Signal Bus
        ~Requests duty calc from~> Duty Service

      Berth Scheduler is a container tech: Node.js
        description: Assigns moorings by draft, tide, and cargo
        -Reads and writes [SQL/TCP]-> Harbor Ledger
        ~Consumes berth events from~> Signal Bus

      Duty Service is a container tech: Python
        description: Calculates cargo duties on incoming loot
        -Reads tariff tables from [SQL/TCP]-> Harbor Ledger

    [Hold]
      Harbor Ledger is a container is a database tech: PostgreSQL
        description: Berths, manifests, tariffs, and toll receipts

      Chart Cache is a container is a cache tech: Redis
        description: Tide tables and berth-availability cache

      Signal Bus is a container is a queue tech: Kafka
        description: Async backbone for berth and duty events

Tide Almanac is a system is an external
  description: Third-party tide tables and storm forecasts

Coin Exchange is a system is an external
  description: Settles doubloon tolls between crews

Pigeon Post is a system is an external
  description: Carrier-pigeon dispatch for harbor notices
